#encoding: utf-8

Feature: Literals7 - List

  Scenario: [1] Return an empty list
    Given any graph
    When executing query:
      """
      RETURN [] AS literal
      """
    Then the result should be, in any order:
      | literal |
      | []      |
    And no side effects

